1.User reports random downtime in webapp hosted in Azure App Services?
A. To investigate random downtime in Azure App Service, I analyze App Service health, logs, and Azure Monitor metrics to identify CPU/memory pressure, app restarts, or platform events. I then use Application Insights to trace failures and address root causes like scaling, memory leaks, or dependency issues.
Hint: logs, manual to auto scale, threshold of cpu,mem - 90% redefined to 80% due to autoscale, Azure monitor metrics, app insights telemetry(metric & traces) 
